Package dictionary

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Dictionary
    Simple customised map interaface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractHashTable
    Abstract implementation of dictionary using hash table.
    ChainedEntry
    A hash table entry that supports chaining.
    Definition
    A Definition repesents a word definition comprising word type (noun, verb, adjective) and description.
    Entry
    Simple datatype for storing a word and its definitions in a hashtable.
    Loader
    Utility for loading a dictionary data from a file.
    LoadTest
    Load performance testing on a hash table
    LPHashTable
    Simple hash table implementation of Dictionary using linear probing.
    Monitorable
    Simple counter type that is intended to be sub classed by hash table implementations to support monitoring of the number of probes that occur during searches.
    QPHashTable
    Simple hash table implementation of Dictionary using quadratic probing.
    SCHashTable
    Simple hash table implementation of Dictionary using sequential chaining.
